        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=TopicQuote&TOPIC_ID=2044&FORUM_ID=2&CAT_ID=1&Forum_Title=General+Discussions&Topic_Title=Comments+from+Rich+Waters+on+casters+Realm"><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height=15 width=15 alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> <BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote> Last week there were a lot of changes made to pets, especially in relation to casting times and reagents.  The current changes on Test Server have almost all pets with a 1.0 second casting time and only 1 reagent required regardless of pet.  Previously pets could take up to 10 seconds or more to cast, and use up to 3 reagents per summoning.  </P><P>Could you provide a little insight into the current pet revamp on test, what your aim is with it, etc?</P><P>The current Test Server changes to pets are mostly regarding casting time. I wanted to see what the impact would be if pets were all fast casting, pretty much guaranteeing that a character could summon his pet almost anytime. There are concerns about things like chain-casting pets and the effect it could have on soloability for instance. The changes on Test should allow us to see the worst case.</P><P>I'm not sure whether this particular change will go live or not. I'll see how it looks, and continue experimenting with other aspects of pets as well. We already put in a feature where pets are almost never riposted to increase their durability, and I'm looking at increasing some resists on pets, as well as their chance to hit against 50+ mobs. We've got some other things we're looking at doing for pets also, but I'm not willing to discuss them until I'm more sure they'll make it onto Test. </P><P>- Rich<BR><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote></P><P>56 DE Necromancer<BR><br><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=49001" target="_blank">Profile</a><BR><a href="http://sizzlesites.com/Ulaa/" target="_blank">Ulaa's web site</a><br><BR><img src="http://www.sizzlesites.com/Ulaa/sig.jpg" border=0></font></td>

